Additional Terms for Educational Use:

This software is specifically designed to support education and may include
features, content, and integrations related to educational curricula, teaching
methodologies, and student learning processes. 

When using this software in educational environments:

1. Student Privacy: All implementations must comply with applicable student
   privacy laws including but not limited to FERPA (US), COPPA (US), and
   relevant Indian data protection regulations.

2. Content Responsibility: Users are responsible for ensuring that any AI-generated
   educational content meets their local educational standards, cultural norms,
   and curriculum requirements.

3. Supervision Required: All student-facing AI features must be deployed with
   appropriate supervision and safety measures as determined by educational
   institutions.

4. Attribution: When distributing modified versions, please maintain attribution
   to the original AI Education Platform project and acknowledge its educational
   purpose.